===Etymology===
{{inh+|et|urj-fin-pro|*asja||matter, case}}, which is of disputed origin:
* Possibly from both {{inh|et|urj-pro|*ate}} and {{m|urj-pro|*-ja}}, from {{inh|et|urj-pro|*-ja}}.
* Possibly from {{inh|et|urj-fin-pro|*asëdak||to live}}, from {{inh|et|urj-pro|*ëśe-}}.
* Possibly borrowed from {{der|et|gem-pro|*uzandiją|*(uz)andiją}}.
